OL,3,CInquest for baby under floorboards to
OL,4,Chear from carbon dating expert
OL,6,FA coroner will hear from a radio-
OL,7,Fcarbon dating expert at the inquest
OL,8,Ffor an unknown baby who was found
OL,9,Fwrapped in a newspaper dating back to
OL,10,F1910.
OL,12,FThe newborn boy's skeleton was
OL,13,Fdiscovered by workmen under
OL,14,Ffloorboards at a property in Bishop
OL,15,FAuckland, County Durham, in 2024, and
OL,16,Fa police investigation was launched.
OL,18,FTwine was found around the infant's
OL,19,Fneck and he had been wrapped in a
OL,20,Fnewspaper called The Umpire.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
