PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779199899
OL,3,CInquest for baby under floorboards to
OL,4,Chear from carbon dating expert
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination revealed the
OL,7,Fbaby was male and carbon dating
OL,8,Fconfirmed that he was born before
OL,9,F1955, but no cause of death could be
OL,10,Festablished.
OL,12,FAn inquest had been due to conclude in
OL,13,FCrook, County Durham, on Monday (18
OL,14,FMay) but coroner Crispin Oliver stated
OL,15,Fhe needed to hear from three witnesses
OL,16,F` from the police investigation, the
OL,17,Fpost-mortem and a radio-carbon dating
OL,18,Fexpert.
OL,20,FThat will now take place on 17
OL,21,FSeptember.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
