PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779199899
OL,3,CInquest for baby under floorboards to
OL,4,Chear from carbon dating expert
OL,6,FMr Oliver said questions about who the
OL,7,Fbaby was, as well as where, when and
OL,8,Fhow he died were all to be considered.
OL,10,FPolice named the infant Baby Auckland
OL,11,Fand a funeral was held last month with
OL,12,Fthe remains buried in a small white
OL,13,Fcasket.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
