PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779199899
OL,3,CInquest for baby under floorboards to
OL,4,Chear from carbon dating expert
OL,6,FAfter the funeral, Cathy Hunt, Durham
OL,7,FCounty Council's cabinet member for
OL,8,Fchildren and young people's services,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Sadly, for reasons we will
OL,10,Fnever know, this little boy was never
OL,11,Fgiven the dignified and appropriate
OL,12,Fburial he deserved, so it was
OL,13,Fimportant that he was laid to rest in
OL,14,Fa way that honoured a life that could
OL,15,Fhave been."
